snippet.title: Best VGM 455 - Zelda: Oracle of Seasons & Ages - Tarm Ruins & Lost Woods
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Gameboy Color
Zelda: Oracle of Seasons & Ages
Tarm Ruins & Lost Woods
